Command> glab mr rebase $1

Argument> $1: [id | branch]

TL;DR> Automatically rebase the source_branch of the merge request against its target_branch

Keywords> gitlab
        > mr

Example01> glab mr rebase 123
Example02> glab mr rebase  # get from current branch
Example03> glab mr rebase branch
Example04> glab mr rebase branch --skip-ci


Reference> https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/cli/-/blob/main/docs/source/mr/rebase.md
